        </p>

        <h3>What cookies do we use?</h3>

        <p>
            We use two types of cookies – session cookies and persistent cookies. Session cookies are temporary files generated on the user’s computer until leaving the webpage or closing an application (web browser). Persistent files remain on the user’s computer for a period specified in the parameters of the cookies or until manually deleted by the user.
        </p>

